                        $('#restaurantname').children('h1').text('The Golden Bull');
                        $('#restaurantname').children('p').text('As an Argentinian Steakhouse, The Golden Bull does not lure you in with extravagance. Their mantra is simple; Beef done well. However, do not be fooled by the apparent simplicity of their dishes. The cooks over at the Golden Bull know what they are doing, and they will make sure you taste that too.');
